-----------------------------
Data Catalogue for Gold Layer
------------------------------

The Gold layer is business level data; that can be used for Analysis purpose.
The data is consumed for reporting and analysis.
For this project star schema is used, in which fact table is centralized source of data and
dimension table

Table 1: gold.dim_customers

Purpose: Stores customer details

Column Name           Data Type          Description
customer_key           INT               Surrogate key uniquely identified each customer record in data tables
customer_id            INT	             Unique numerical identifier assigned to each customer
customer_number        NVARCHAR(50)      Alphanumeric identifier representing customer data for tracing and locaing 
first_name             NVARCHAR(50)      Customers first name from database
last_name              NVARCHAR(50)      Customers last name 
country                NVARCHAR(50)      country of residence
marital_status         NVARCHAR(50)      marital status M for married , S for single
gender                 NVARCHAR(50)      gender of customer M for male, F for female
birthdate	             DATE	             date of birth of customer
create_date            DATE	             The date and time when the customer record was created

Table 2: gold.dim_products
Purpose: Stores product details
Column Name           Data Type          Description
product_key             INT              Surrogate key uniquely identified each product record in data tables
product_id              INT	             Unique numerical identifier assigned to each product for tracking and referencing
product_number         NVARCHAR(50)      Alphanumeric identifier code representing product used for categorization and inventory 
category_id            NVARCHAR(50)      Identifier for products category
category               NVARCHAR(50)      descriptive name of the product
subcategory            NVARCHAR(50)      country of residence
maintenance_required   NVARCHAR(50)      Indicates where product requires management
cost                   NVARCHAR(50)      Cost Price of product
product_line           DATE	             specific product line or series to which product belongs
start_date             DATE	             The date and time when the product became available for sale or use

Table 3: gold.fact_sales
Purpose Stores transactional details data for analytical purposes
Column Name              Data Type        Description
order_number             NVARCHAR(50)     Unique identifier for each sales order
product_key               INT	            Surrogate key for linking the order to product table 
customer_key              INT             Surrogate key for linking the order to customer table 
order_date                DATE            Date of order placed
shipping_date             DATE            Date of order shipping
due_date                  DATE            Date when order payment is fulfilled
sales_amount              INT             The total amount of order
quantity                  INT             Quantity of the product ordered
price                     INT             Price per unit of product
